name: Wicket (V)
Lore: 'Ewok scout. Son of Shodu and Deej. Found Leia and befriended her. Persuaded his tribe to help.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor. Once per game, may use 3 Force to release a Rebel captive present on Endor. During your deploy phase, may use 1 Force to deploy an Ewok weapon or a unique (•) Ewok from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
